00:40:34.867 --> 00:40:37.633
We talked earlier about the
Greenland ice sheet

00:40:37.633 --> 00:40:39.467
reducing its mass.

00:40:39.467 --> 00:40:42.233
Sea level rise I showed
you that diagram here.

00:40:42.233 --> 00:40:45.133
Stratospheric cooling,
and the deciduous

00:40:45.133 --> 00:40:47.233
growing season is longer.

00:40:47.233 --> 00:40:51.567
So all those changes have been
noted over the 20th century,

00:40:51.567 --> 00:40:59.833
especially over the last
25 or 30 years or so.

00:40:59.833 --> 00:41:04.900
Well, this has not stayed in
the scientific community,

00:41:04.900 --> 00:41:06.333
these issues.

00:41:06.333 --> 00:41:09.167
You read about global warming
today everywhere.

00:41:09.167 --> 00:41:13.667
And I had great fun spent a
